data.description: Discover the perfect 2-bedroom (plus den), 2-full bath sanctuary in the heart of White Marsh with this immaculate 1st-floor unit. As you enter through the inviting foyer, you'll be greeted by elegant crown molding throughout. The spacious living room and dining room combo boasts high-end plush carpeting, creating a cozy and inviting space for relaxation. The kitchen, remodeled just one year ago, showcases Carrera marble floors, sleek quartz countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Abundant counter space and the convenience of a washer and dryer within the kitchen make this space as practical as it is beautiful. Additionally, this unit features an office, providing an ideal space for work or creative endeavors. The primary suite comes complete with an attached bath and a generous walk-in closet, offering ample storage and personal comfort. The second bedroom also offers a full bath, ensuring privacy and convenience for all. Step outside to the covered porch/terrace, a lovely spot to enjoy the outdoors or entertain guests. This property offers a blend of modern upgrades and timeless charm, making it a true gem in the White Marsh area.
